videos.headline: Britain Covey breaks loose for 19-yard Utah TD
videos.description: Britain Covey hauls in a pass and speeds away from the Ohio State defense for a 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Britain Covey breaks loose for 19-yard Utah TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Micah Bernard makes superb catch in the corner of end zone for Utah TD
videos.description: Cam Rising lofts a pass to Micah Bernard, who keeps the one foot in bounds for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Micah Bernard makes superb catch in the corner of end zone for Utah TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stroud drops absolute dime to Egbuka for 30-yard gain
videos.description: C.J. Stroud drops a beautiful throw to Emeka Egbuka, who manages to haul the catch in bounds for a big gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stroud drops absolute dime to Egbuka for 30-yard gain) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: C.J. Stroud drops dime to Marvin Harrison Jr. for an Ohio State TD
videos.description: C.J. Stroud lofts a perfect throw to Marvin Harrison Jr. on fourth down for a 25-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (C.J. Stroud drops dime to Marvin Harrison Jr. for an Ohio State TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State's Sawyer ejected for targeting after hit on Rising
videos.description: Ohio State's Jack Sawyer is ejected for targeting after lowering his head for a big hit on Utah quarterback Cam Rising.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio State's Sawyer ejected for targeting after hit on Rising) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tavion Thomas walks into end zone for easy Utah TD
videos.description: Tavion Thomas takes the handoff and easily gets into the end zone for a 6-yard Utah touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tavion Thomas walks into end zone for easy Utah TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith-Njigba stiff-arms corner down sideline for 50-yard TD
videos.description: C.J. Stroud finds Jaxon Smith-Njigba, who hauls it in and stiff-arms a defender for a 50-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith-Njigba stiff-arms corner down sideline for 50-yard TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Britain Covey makes house call on 97-yard kickoff return for TD
videos.description: Utah's Britain Covey takes the kickoff and weaves through traffic for a 97-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Britain Covey makes house call on 97-yard kickoff return for TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith-Njigba speeds away from Utah defense for 52-yard OSU TD
videos.description: C.J. Stroud finds Jaxon Smith-Njigba in stride for a 52-yard touchdown, giving Stroud three TDs on three consecutive passes.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith-Njigba speeds away from Utah defense for 52-yard OSU TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cameron Rising somehow stays on his feet for 62-yard Utah TD
videos.description: Cameron Rising keeps it on fourth down and breaks multiple tackles on a 62-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cameron Rising somehow stays on his feet for 62-yard Utah TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith-Njigba fumbles into end zone to give Utah the ball back
videos.description: Jaxon Smith-Njigba thinks he has a touchdown, but Utah's Clark Phillips III hustles back and knocks it loose for a fumble into the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith-Njigba fumbles into end zone to give Utah the ball back) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Utah, Ohio State combine for 5 TDs in under 3 minutes at Rose Bowl
videos.description: Utah and Ohio State light up the Rose Bowl with five touchdowns in 2 minutes and 31 seconds of game time.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah, Ohio State combine for 5 TDs in under 3 minutes at Rose Bowl) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clark Phillips picks off C.J. Stroud in the end zone
videos.description: C.J. Stroud tries the fade route to the end zone, but Clark Phillips III gets in front of the wide receiver for a Utah interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clark Phillips picks off C.J. Stroud in the end zone) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Utah punter's dropped snap sets OSU up with great field position
videos.description: Utah punter Michael Williams drops the snap, giving the Buckeyes the ball inside the red zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah punter's dropped snap sets OSU up with great field position) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: C.J. Stroud and Marvin Harrison Jr. link up for a 2nd TD connection
videos.description: C.J. Stroud calmly finds Marvin Harrison Jr. in the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (C.J. Stroud and Marvin Harrison Jr. link up for a 2nd TD connection) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith-Njigba breaks Ohio State's program record for receiving yards in game
videos.description: Jaxon Smith-Njigba hauls in the catch, giving him the record for most receiving yards in a game in Ohio State history.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith-Njigba breaks Ohio State's program record for receiving yards in game) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Marvin Harrison Jr. ties Rose Bowl with 3rd TD catch
videos.description: Marvin Harrison Jr. beats his man off the line and C.J. Stroud finds him for the touchdown, tying the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Marvin Harrison Jr. ties Rose Bowl with 3rd TD catch) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cameron Rising leaves Rose Bowl after hitting his head on the ground
videos.description: Cameron Rising walks off the field after falling on his head while taking a sack.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cameron Rising leaves Rose Bowl after hitting his head on the ground) 2022/01/01

videos.headline: Smith-Njibga's amazing over-the-shoulder TD catch gives OSU lead
videos.description: C.J. Stroud throws a perfect ball to Jaxon Smith-Njigba for the touchdown late in the fourth, giving the Buckeyes their first lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith-Njibga's amazing over-the-shoulder TD catch gives OSU lead) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Utah ties it after backup QB Barnes finds Kincaid for TD
videos.description: Utah backup quarterback Bryson Barnes finds Dalton Kincaid for a 15-yard touchdown, tying the score at 45.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Utah ties it after backup QB Barnes finds Kincaid for TD) 2022/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Noah Ruggles wins Rose Bowl for Ohio State with late field goal
videos.description: Noah Ruggles' 19-yard field goal is the deciding score for Ohio State in a 48-45 win over Utah in the Rose Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Noah Ruggles wins Rose Bowl for Ohio State with late field goal) 2022/01/01 ESHEET
